commits.commitMessage:
FWINT-689 - Adjustments required for rfnvugenerator.exe

Description:
- use pyinstaller.exe --onefile rfnvugenerator.py command
to produce a stand-alone executable out of .py file
- add import clause to address run-time failures.
- excluded ability to send mail due to missing MIMEText library
- add the unified executable reflecting above changes
- update the readme to reflect the executable renaming

Resolves: FWINT-689
Change-Id: Ib01f57ed9923dad32021feee2b4cd3645b7f79a6
commits.subject: FWINT-689 - Adjustments required for rfnvugenerator.exe
